XLOG - Extended logging

Syntax:   XLOG=<on/off>
Response: none

Settable parameters:
<on/off>: ON to turn on extended logging, OFF to turn off. Default
          OFF. When OFF, commands issued from within procedures are
          not logged and ACK responses from modules are not logged.
          All responses are always logged. When ON, all commands
          and responses are logged.

      Comments: Immediate execution operator command.
